{"id": "1191250216104497192", "channel_id": "1191250216104497192", "type": 0, "author_id": "415146558271651841", "author_name": "ascrep8141", "author_bot": false, "content": "這封信超可愛的，很想把他放進郵件珍藏箱，但似乎沒有可以自己設定哪些信要進珍藏箱的功能QQ\n如果已經有這功能的話，想麻煩幫忙解惑具體位置跟使用方法；如果沒有的話有點希望可以新增這功能，謝謝～", "timestamp": "2024-01-01T05:23:03.878000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [{"id": "1191250216276480072", "filename": "Screenshot_20240101_131747.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 105562, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1191250216104497192/1191250216276480072/Screenshot_20240101_131747.jpg?ex=69ccabb7&is=69cb5a37&hm=d066264a8df89bd4b6640d7a5376c9662c5e46932bfb01546dcc490ac58d2682&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1191250216104497192", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」希望可以把這封信放進珍藏箱", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1191369195083026502", "channel_id": "1191369195083026502", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181025751710056449", "author_name": "0sgtq0", "author_bot": false, "content": "我被小怪打成1血后，踩1次格子发现不扣血后估计踩格子去商店。\n在我重商店前往 boss路上最后一个扣血格子就直接死了，没有弹出复活界面\n\n如果是bug那么我就不该死\n如果是机制，那么起码应该弹出复活界面\n提示下\n\n哦对了，我没有应急感知体 可能是这个原因？", "timestamp": "2024-01-01T13:15:50.677000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1191369195263377439", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-01-01-21-05-41-519_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 102346, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1191369195083026502/1191369195263377439/Screenshot_2024-01-01-21-05-41-519_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cc71c6&is=69cb2046&hm=620cf45b434d46c8a103a473ccf513883b3252ec7b2e0db69b36960d7e86ee3b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1191369195083026502", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」1血踩扣血格子4-5次后会直接死亡退出", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1181168158678204497"]}
